      "message": "nit: names \"blameLength\" and \"blameSize\" are very similar and it is hard to tell what\u0027s the difference.\nit is definitely not obvious form the name that size is synchronized and length is not\n\nperhaps we don\u0027t need blameLength if we use mutex above",
